Class OsnAttributeLookupLovConverter

java.lang.Object
  oracle.apps.fnd.applcore.oaext.osn.publicutil.converter.OsnFieldValueConverter
      oracle.apps.fnd.applcore.oaext.osn.publicutil.converter.lookup.OsnAttributeLookupLovConverter

public class OsnAttributeLookupLovConverter
extends OsnFieldValueConverter

A converter which looks up the LOV display value for the attribute being converted. If the attribute being converted does not have an associated LOV then an OsnConversionException will be thrown. There are no parameters for this converter.

See OsnFieldValueConverter javadoc for more information on how to consume converters and the other override options.
